@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(v2))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.83 + v2 + 0.18)) / ((v1 + 0.11 + v0 + 0.51) / 0.47))
    tmp = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.41 * v2 + 0.47) / 0.31))
    v0 = wp.exp((0.11 * (tmp + 0.50 * tmp + 0.06)))
    tmp = (0.05 / 0.96)
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.46)) - wp.exp((v0 + 0.71 / tmp + 0.41)))
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.14 / v2 + 0.77)) / 0.96)
    data[tid] = v0
